#MEM id=rules source=/root/yvon/agent-department/Technical/mia/skills/design-and-build/vercel-react-best-practices/rules/rerender-no-inline-components.md
M|rules|title: Don't Define Components Inside Components
M|rules|impact: HIGH
M|rules|impactDescription: prevents remount on every render
M|rules|tags: rerender, components, remount, performance
M|rules|**Impact: HIGH (prevents remount on every render)**
M|rules|Defining a component inside another component creates a new component type on every render. React sees a different component each time and fully remounts it, destroying all state and DOM.
M|rules|A common reason developers do this is to access parent variables without passing props. Always pass props instead.
M|rules|**Incorrect (remounts on every render):**
M|rules|```tsx
M|rules|function UserProfile({ user, theme }) {
M|rules|// Defined inside to access `theme` - BAD
M|rules|const Avatar = () => (
M|rules|<img
M|rules|src={user.avatarUrl}
M|rules|className={theme === 'dark' ? 'avatar-dark' : 'avatar-light'}
M|rules|/>
M|rules|)
M|rules|// Defined inside to access `user` - BAD
M|rules|const Stats = () => (
M|rules|<div>
M|rules|<span>{user.followers} followers</span>
M|rules|<span>{user.posts} posts</span>
M|rules|</div>
M|rules|)
M|rules|return (
M|rules|<div>
M|rules|<Avatar />
M|rules|<Stats />
M|rules|</div>
M|rules|)
M|rules|}
M|rules|```
M|rules|Every time `UserProfile` renders, `Avatar` and `Stats` are new component types. React unmounts the old instances and mounts new ones, losing any internal state, running effects again, and recreating D
M|rules|**Correct (pass props instead):**
M|rules|```tsx
M|rules|function Avatar({ src, theme }: { src: string; theme: string }) {
M|rules|return (
M|rules|<img
M|rules|src={src}
M|rules|className={theme === 'dark' ? 'avatar-dark' : 'avatar-light'}
M|rules|/>
M|rules|)
M|rules|}
M|rules|function Stats({ followers, posts }: { followers: number; posts: number }) {
M|rules|return (
M|rules|<div>
M|rules|<span>{followers} followers</span>
M|rules|<span>{posts} posts</span>
M|rules|</div>
M|rules|)
M|rules|}
M|rules|function UserProfile({ user, theme }) {
M|rules|return (
M|rules|<div>
M|rules|<Avatar src={user.avatarUrl} theme={theme} />
M|rules|<Stats followers={user.followers} posts={user.posts} />
M|rules|</div>
M|rules|)
M|rules|}
M|rules|```
M|rules|**Symptoms of this bug:**
M|rules|- Input fields lose focus on every keystroke
M|rules|- Animations restart unexpectedly
M|rules|- `useEffect` cleanup/setup runs on every parent render
M|rules|- Scroll position resets inside the component